Question: >
  "The rapid development of artificial intelligence has inevitably altered the landscape of modern education, prompting both enthusiasm and skepticism among scholars."
  What is the main idea of the sentence above?
Answer: AI development has brought changes and mixed reactions in education.
Explanation: >
  Kalimat utama menyoroti dua hal: perubahan dalam pendidikan akibat AI dan reaksi campuran (antusiasme dan skeptisisme) dari para akademisi. Pilihan yang mencakup kedua gagasan ini adalah yang paling tepat.
Options:
  - Text: AI is entirely harmful to modern education systems.
  - Text: AI development has brought changes and mixed reactions in education.
  - Text: Scholars are unanimously enthusiastic about AI.
  - Text: Education landscapes change only because of technological constraints.
  - Text: Skepticism is the only reaction scholars have towards AI.
