  "The manager demanded that the new policy _____ implemented immediately without any further delay."
  Which word best completes the subjunctive sentence?
Answer: be
Explanation: >
  Kalimat tersebut menggunakan present subjunctive yang ditandai dengan kata kerja 'demanded that'. Aturan subjunctive mengharuskan kata kerja dasar (bare infinitive), sehingga to be yang digunakan adalah 'be'.
Options:
  - Text: is
  - Text: was
  - Text: to be
  - Text: are
  - Text: be
