Question: >
  "Scarcely had she finished reading the letter when the telephone rang."
  What does the sentence imply?
Answer: She finished reading the letter right before the telephone rang.
Explanation: >
  Struktur inversi 'Scarcely ... when' digunakan untuk menyatakan bahwa satu kejadian terjadi segera setelah kejadian lain selesai. Ini sama maknanya dengan kejadian pertama selesai tepat sebelum kejadian kedua.
Options:
  - Text: The telephone rang before she started reading the letter.
  - Text: She finished reading the letter right before the telephone rang.
  - Text: She was reading the letter while answering the phone.
  - Text: The telephone rang, so she stopped reading the letter.
  - Text: She did not finish the letter because of the telephone.
