Question: >
  "If the company had invested more in cybersecurity, the massive data breach would not have occurred."
  Based on the conditional sentence, what is the actual reality?
Answer: The company did not invest enough in cybersecurity, so the breach occurred.
Explanation: >
  Kalimat ini adalah Third Conditional yang menyatakan situasi imajiner di masa lampau. Fakta dari kalimat ini selalu berlawanan dengan pernyataannya: perusahaan tidak berinvestasi cukup, sehingga kebocoran data terjadi.
Options:
  - Text: The company invested enough in cybersecurity to prevent the breach.
  - Text: The data breach did not occur because of good investments.
  - Text: The company did not invest enough in cybersecurity, so the breach occurred.
  - Text: The breach will occur if they do not invest in cybersecurity.
  - Text: The company is currently investing heavily to avoid a breach.
