Question: >
  Identify the sentences that contain grammatically correct conditional clauses.
Explanation: >
  Kalimat kondisional yang benar harus mengikuti aturan tense: Type 1 (Present + Future), Type 2 (Past + Would V1), Type 3 (Past Perfect + Would Have V3), atau bentuk inversi yang sesuai.
