  - Text: "If she wasn't so afraid of flying, she would have traveled to Paris last week." (Kondisi masa kini berakibat ke masa lalu).
    IsCorrect: Benar
  - Text: "If they won the lottery yesterday, they will be rich now." (Ini bukan pola mixed conditional yang tepat).
    IsCorrect: Benar
