Explanation: >
  Mixed conditional menghubungkan kejadian lampau yang tidak nyata dengan akibat yang dirasakan di masa kini (If + Past Perfect, Subject + would + V1).
Options:
  - Text: "If I had finished my assignment last night, I could relax now."
