  Jika subjeknya indefinite pronoun (everyone, someone, nobody), maka pronoun pada tag-nya menggunakan "they". Perhatikan bahwa nobody/nothing sudah bernilai negatif.
Options:
  - Text: "Everyone passed the exam, didn't they?"
    IsCorrect: Benar
  - Text: "Nothing can go wrong, can it?"
    IsCorrect: Benar
  - Text: "Somebody left their bag here, didn't he?"
    IsCorrect: Salah
  - Text: "Nobody called while I was out, did they?"
    IsCorrect: Benar
---
