Question: >
  Tentukan Benar atau Salah penggunaan pola Causative ("Get" dan "Have") di bawah ini.
Explanation: >
  Pola Causative Pasif selalu "Have/Get + Object (benda) + V3". Pola Aktif "Get + orang + To V1". Pola Aktif "Have + orang + V1".
Options:
  - Text: "I will get the mechanic to check my brakes tomorrow."
    IsCorrect: Benar
  - Text: "She had her expensive dress dry-cleaned."
    IsCorrect: Benar
  - Text: "He got his assistant prepare the meeting room." (Get aktif harus menggunakan to-infinitive).
    IsCorrect: Salah
  - Text: "We had the plumber to fix the leaking pipe." (Have aktif harus menggunakan bare infinitive).
    IsCorrect: Salah
