Question: >
  Tentukan Benar atau Salah untuk struktur "Third Conditional" (Kondisional Tipe 3) berikut.
Explanation: >
  Kondisional tipe 3 merujuk pada masa lalu yang tidak bisa diubah. Pola: If + Past Perfect, Subject + would/could/might + have + V3.
Options:
  - Text: "If I had woke up earlier, I wouldn't have missed the flight." (Woke adalah V2, seharusnya V3 'woken').
    IsCorrect: Salah
  - Text: "If she had seen the warning sign, she would have stopped the car."
    IsCorrect: Benar
  - Text: "Had they known about the traffic jam, they would have taken a different route." (Inversi klausa If ini benar).
    IsCorrect: Benar
  - Text: "If he would have studied harder, he would have passed the exam." (Tidak boleh ada 'would' di dalam klausa 'If').
    IsCorrect: Salah
