Question: >
  Evaluasi kebenaran perubahan dari kalimat Direct Speech ke Indirect Speech.
  Direct: "Don't touch the broken glass!" she told him.
Explanation: >
  Kalimat perintah/larangan dalam Indirect Speech menggunakan pola "tell/ask + object + not to + infinitive".
Options:
  - Text: She told him don't touch the broken glass.
    IsCorrect: Salah
  - Text: She told him not to touch the broken glass.
    IsCorrect: Benar
  - Text: She said to him to not touch the broken glass.
    IsCorrect: Salah
  - Text: She warned him not to touch the broken glass.
    IsCorrect: Benar
